            <h4>How to get there</h4>
            <p>Daily flights to Cagayan de Oro from Manila, Cebu and Davao have made travel easier to reach Malaybalay City. Ships and ferries are also scheduled daily bounding to Cagayan de Oro City.</p>
            <p>Just 91 kilometers from Cagayan de Oro City, Malaybalay City can be reached by bus which is available 24 hours. Buses from Davao and the southern provinces of Mindanao also ply the Bukidnon route with a convenient stop-over in Malaybalay. Air conditioned buses and vans are also avail- able for those who choose maximum travel comfort.</p>
